name: WEST Neon T-shirt
description: This straight-cut t-shirt for men is made of pre-shrunk and ring-spun cotton. Its high quality and fashioning shows in terms of double-thread seams on its cuffs and hem as well as its double-bevelled collar edges (1X1 ribbing). A collar neckband makes for a comfortable fit. Fabric weight 190g/sqm. 100% cotton. T-Shirt is available in many different colours. Also you can get the crown in many different colours. Please contact me for more details.

name: WEST Drawstring bag
description: We couldn't think of an easier way to transport your sport essentials. You can stuff almost 3 gallons (11 liters) worth of gear into this little bag. It is super light, water resistant and will do exactly what you think it would â€“ nothing more or less. In a jiffy, you can tie up your little bundle with drawstring cords that are attached to the bag's sides. String it to your back like a rucksack, and off you go. Now you have your hands free to ride a bike or buy a bus ticket. 100% polyester. The bag and the crown are available in many different colours. Contact me for more details.
